"""
=============================================================
  Stock Price Prediction using LSTM
  Industry: Finance
  Tools: Python, Pandas, TensorFlow/Keras, Matplotlib
=============================================================

Description:
    This script predicts future stock prices using historical
    price data and technical indicators (Moving Average, RSI).
    An LSTM (Long Short-Term Memory) neural network is trained
    on time-series sequences to forecast the next closing price.

Steps:
    1. Collect / load historical stock price data
    2. Calculate technical indicators (MA, RSI)
    3. Preprocess: normalize data, create time-series sequences
    4. Train an LSTM model
    5. Evaluate with RMSE and backtest against historical data
    6. Visualize predictions vs. actual prices

Dataset:
    Yahoo Finance (via yfinance) or Kaggle Stock Data.
    Install yfinance: pip install yfinance

Usage:
    python stock_price_prediction.py
"""

